title: Sumobrottning
description:
Pull the suit over your head and step into someone else's body, master the body check and start wrestling. In the summer queen, your big dressed hut meets another big dressed hut, with the only rule of being the one who first crashes his opponent. Sumo Queen, who originally comes from Japan, has now gone to Marholmen for your girlfriend or bridal shower. Or if you want to play in other forms, like with friends, family or during the party party.

Sumo Queen Tournament fits the larger groups and we have six summons that you can easily cross over your head, then you're ready for a match.

Price: 360 kr / per ink VAT (288 kr / per ex.moms) My deb10 persons
